label.phrase: it was clear that this bill was necessary when our subcommittee learned at a hearing in june 2007 that an fps security guard contractor had failed to pay 600 d c area federal security officers and to make other important benefit payments to pensions health benefits and the like our subcommittee intervened when an action by the fps and the immigration and customs enforcement bureau a division of dhs where fps is placed was reported to us
